{"tid":94653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"太多遊客在大屠殺紀念碑開心自拍「打卡」　德國藝術家 PS 改圖諷刺","createTime":"2017-01-25T11:24:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T08:33:43.000Z","uid":35519,"like":58,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"788bd816917f60770f686be8c6bdf5a330441974","tid":94653,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T11:24:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>太多遊客在大屠殺紀念碑開心自拍「打卡」<br />\n德國藝術家 PS 改圖諷刺</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">作者：YUI ON</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/181014/%E5%A4%AA%E5%A4%9A%E9%81%8A%E5%AE%A2%E5%9C%A8%E5%A4%A7%E5%B1%A0%E6%AE%BA%E7%B4%80%E5%BF%B5%E7%A2%91%E9%96%8B%E5%BF%83%E8%87%AA%E6%8B%8D%E3%80%8C%E6%89%93%E5%8D%A1%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%8C%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2F181014%2F%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25A4%259A%25E9%2581%258A%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%259C%25A8%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B1%25A0%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E7%25B4%2580%25E5%25BF%25B5%25E7%25A2%2591%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25BF%2583%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%258B%258D%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%258D%25A1%25E3%2580%258D%25EF%25BC%258C%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%259C%258B&d=%2BLAOwWMB1dqzkVwaUobaemN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=d6cc8747\" target=\"_blank\">http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/181014/%E5%A4%AA%E5%A4%9A%E9%81%8A%E5%AE%A2%E5%9C%A8%E5%A4%A7%E5%B1%A0%E6%AE%BA%E7%B4%80%E5%BF%B5%E7%A2%91%E9%96%8B%E5%BF%83%E8%87%AA%E6%8B%8D%E3%80%8C%E6%89%93%E5%8D%A1%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%8C%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Shahak-Shapira.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2FShahak-Shapira.jpg&h=35cbe4a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n德國藝術家 Shahak Shapira 在過去幾年中發現到一個有趣現像，就是一些遊客會在柏林大屠殺紀念碑（Denkmal fur die ermordeten Juden Europas）中開心自拍，或是踏上那裡的石碑做著各種動作拍照，所以他就把這些自拍照 PS 成諷刺作品「Yolocaust」。<br />\n<br />\n遊人所拍攝的紀念碑由約 3,000 塊混凝土板組成，是建築師 Peter Eisenman 設計，象徵被殺害、埋住的 600 萬猶太人，在附加的石板中列出猶太大屠殺紀念館（Yad Vashem Sanctuary）得到的所有已知受害猶太人的名字。由於大屠殺對一些德國人而言是可恥的，也是人類一個黑暗歷史，所以 Shahak Shapira 認為，在有著這樣意義的地點中，應該抱有最基本的尊重，而不是看到建築物設計很「有趣」，就無視地點去開心自拍。「這裡不是什麼聖地，當發現人們在這裡開心『打卡』的照片愈來愈多，我就覺得應該做點什麼，來提醒人大屠殺紀念碑的真正意義。」<br />\n<br />\n大家可以看看，由於使用了當年的集中營照片 PS，部份可能令人不安：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Shahak-Shapira14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2FShahak-Shapira14.jpg&h=ffb15c37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Shahak-Shapira22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2FShahak-Shapira22.jpg&h=00536975&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Shahak-Shapira10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2FShahak-Shapira10.jpg&h=7bfb52cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Shahak-Shapira16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2FShahak-Shapira16.jpg&h=bd945b4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Shahak-Shapira18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2FShahak-Shapira18.jpg&h=a81e4978&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Shahak-Shapira6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2FShahak-Shapira6.jpg&h=38f693ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Shahak-Shapira8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2FShahak-Shapira8.jpg&h=2d7c81de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Shahak-Shapira12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2FShahak-Shapira12.jpg&h=39de55b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Shahak-Shapira20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2FShahak-Shapira20.jpg&h=42766e08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Shahak-Shapira24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2FShahak-Shapira24.jpg&h=c63c60f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Shahak-Shapira4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2FShahak-Shapira4.jpg&h=7ad39491&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nThe images were all on public social media accounts and he didn't seek permission from any of the account holders. At the bottom of the site is an email address - &quot;<a href=\"http://undouche.me\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fundouche.me&d=%2BLAOwWMB1dqzkVwaUobaemN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=44e2d25f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">undouche.me</a>@yolocaust.de&quot; - to request that an image be removed.<br />\n<br />\n這樣的做法，當然會在網上引起爭議，雖然網民普遍都支持藝術家的控訴 / 諷刺方式，但也有人覺得不應該就這樣用別人的照片 PS、可能會讓相中人被其他網民「起底」或攻擊等等，引起仇恨。同時，人雖然是有做任何事情的自由，但是否應該在嚴肅的場合玩耍（藝術家指有人還會在石碑上野餐）、人們對於這樣的歷史，是否有足夠的了解（因為無知所以才走去自拍？），也是值得反思的。"},{"pid":"f71dce12f5576198643b99aabc8065eb2b69da99","tid":94653,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T11:25:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"http://yolocaust.de/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyolocaust.de%2F&d=%2BLAOwWMB1dqzkVwaUobaemN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=7710081d\" target=\"_blank\">http://yolocaust.de/</a></span>"},{"pid":"ad15c5a1337c471ee4eab69a8c7aa886d6ebaaf8","tid":94653,"uid":42299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T11:32:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"627bbc659dfbb814d0497e72833c4cb3993c65f6","tid":94653,"uid":31752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T11:35:23.000Z","msg":"懷念爺爺"},{"pid":"0a80d6e52a7a7f87063ee8062dd632040e209cab","tid":94653,"uid":12222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T11:37:06.000Z","msg":"其實點解睇呢啲事一定要用一個好嚴肅既態度<br />\n其實愈沈重咁對待愈放唔底歷史包袱<br />\n唔係話要恥笑心態睇<br />\n但用一個正面睇法睇真係有咁大問題咩<br />\n利申以前中學有個德國交換生<br />\n一直都唔敢同佢傾歷史"},{"pid":"2fbb79cae6ed894e65d86565b7606d9f34854c71","tid":94653,"uid":807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T11:38:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實點解睇呢啲事一定要用一個好嚴肅既態度<br />\n其實愈沈重咁對待愈放唔底歷史包袱<br />\n唔係話要恥笑心態睇<br />\n但用一個正面睇法睇真係有咁大問題咩<br />\n利申以前中學有個德國交換生<br />\n一直都唔敢同佢傾歷史</blockquote><br />\nagger<br />\n垃圾左膠"},{"pid":"674db157dbf8a418cb28ccbc8498ea82eaecebd5","tid":94653,"uid":62464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T11:40:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">在有著這樣意義的地點中，應該抱有最基本的尊重，而不是看到建築物設計很「有趣」，就無視地點去開心自拍。「這裡不是什麼聖地</span><br />\n<br />\n佢講得岩，設計既原意係紀念死去既人，並唔係比大家用黎當佢係一個有趣既地方，跪係到玩倒立同拋波個兩個都有啲唔尊重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac676b72e1f028e8edc5bf19145d19402ba48241","tid":94653,"uid":25916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T11:43:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實點解睇呢啲事一定要用一個好嚴肅既態度<br />\n其實愈沈重咁對待愈放唔底歷史包袱<br />\n唔係話要恥笑心態睇<br />\n但用一個正面睇法睇真係有咁大問題咩<br />\n利申以前中學有個德國交換生<br />\n一直都唔敢同佢傾歷史</blockquote><br />\nagger<br />\n垃圾左膠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你會唔會係墳場自拍打卡 個度都算d無名氏半個墳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b7adb13f94f0b32b6135807735c50de426e766","tid":94653,"uid":30510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T11:44:04.000Z","msg":"唔該改埋係天安門自拍嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0df359c044d20f3bae33ce26f1896b691d97d247","tid":94653,"uid":35630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T11:44:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實點解睇呢啲事一定要用一個好嚴肅既態度<br />\n其實愈沈重咁對待愈放唔底歷史包袱<br />\n唔係話要恥笑心態睇<br />\n但用一個正面睇法睇真係有咁大問題咩<br />\n利申以前中學有個德國交換生<br />\n一直都唔敢同佢傾歷史</blockquote><br />\n但我又唔認為相中人知d石碑係咩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f8d154e397801cc2de5eb930c95244b48739ecb","tid":94653,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T11:44:51.000Z","msg":"反而 我覺得重仆街, 重提事件萬人坑. <br />\n自拍還自拍你提一提就得."},{"pid":"bb307e14dcd7939c8b7f85b423a15a628962444b","tid":94653,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T11:45:03.000Z","msg":"d圖又幾好笑"},{"pid":"518d74bf4acfa44896f48e82b7fab383bb0bda94","tid":94653,"uid":47352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T11:53:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實點解睇呢啲事一定要用一個好嚴肅既態度<br />\n其實愈沈重咁對待愈放唔底歷史包袱<br />\n唔係話要恥笑心態睇<br />\n但用一個正面睇法睇真係有咁大問題咩<br />\n利申以前中學有個德國交換生<br />\n一直都唔敢同佢傾歷史</blockquote><br />\nagger<br />\n垃圾左膠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你會唔會係墳場自拍打卡 個度都算d無名氏半個墳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無話一定要好嚴肅 但至少要尊重"},{"pid":"055dfba61baedd89b9cf899236e649ee3d52ed1b","tid":94653,"uid":47352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T11:56:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\nagger<br />\n垃圾左膠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你會唔會係墳場自拍打卡 個度都算d無名氏半個墳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無話一定要好嚴肅 但至少要尊重</blockquote><br />\n//在有著這樣意義的地點中，應該抱有最基本的尊重，而不是看到建築物設計很「有趣」，就無視地點去開心自拍。「這裡不是什麼聖地，當發現人們在這裡開心『打卡』的照片愈來愈多，我就覺得應該做點什麼，來提醒人大屠殺紀念碑的真正意義。」<br />\n如果成班女覺得咁多塊石碑好似大磚好得意而影相自拍，咁其實你唔使特登去嗰度"},{"pid":"9bd3e0067be2eb72d1b36c748d639492df275714","tid":94653,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T11:57:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實點解睇呢啲事一定要用一個好嚴肅既態度<br />\n其實愈沈重咁對待愈放唔底歷史包袱<br />\n唔係話要恥笑心態睇<br />\n但用一個正面睇法睇真係有咁大問題咩<br />\n利申以前中學有個德國交換生<br />\n一直都唔敢同佢傾歷史</blockquote><br />\nagger<br />\n垃圾左膠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你會唔會係墳場自拍打卡 個度都算d無名氏半個墳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無話一定要好嚴肅 但至少要尊重</blockquote><br />\n你試下去墳場打卡都唔比人屌先咁講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d039ca79968e84a6d43911fc3110db98c1ed37f6","tid":94653,"uid":24547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T11:58:30.000Z","msg":"Shahak Shapira (@ShahakShapira) | Twitter<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com&d=%2BLAOwWMB1dqzkVwaUobaemN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=0cb7c9e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com</a> &rsaquo; shahakshapira<br />\nThe latest Tweets from Shahak Shapira (@ ShahakShapira). Shahak Shapira is <span style=\"color: red;\">Israeli</span>, Berliner and owns a regular-sized Penis. His hobbies are Hummus, Death ...<br />\n原來如此"},{"pid":"b444584b8775f9c4d848e28f4fe9630b9fefd7c5","tid":94653,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T12:08:14.000Z","msg":"又膠上腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\